The Telegraph - Calcutta : International

 World Briefs

 Gaza on the boil 

 Gaza, May 17 (Reuters): Israel launched air strikes in Gaza on Thursday against a Hamas security force, killing at least four people. 

 Israel said it launched the raids in response to cross-border rocket attacks. 

 Japan firing 

 Nagakute, Japan (Reuters): A Japanese policeman died on Friday after being shot by a gunman who had earlier injured his son and daughter and taken a woman hostage. 

 Paris jail 

 Los Angeles (Reuters): Paris Hilton will only be jailed for 23 days of a 45-day sentence for a driving offence . 




